      <definition id="3805">
        <method>rubric</method>
        <name>DAOM-EL Discussion Forum Rubric</name>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;font-family:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"&gt;Grades on discussion posts are determined by a collective score on all posts for the unit in three areas: quality, quantity, and timeliness. The weighting for quality is double, making quality the most important factor in determining the grade. The rubric below describes the level of participation required for each score. The term "original posts" refers to posts that address the discussion topic directly. The term "responses" refers to posts in response to others' original posts or questions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Â &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grade for each unit:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;15 points = 100%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;14 points = 93%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;13 points = 87%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;12 points = 80%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;11 points = 73%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;10 points = 67%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;9 points = 60%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;8 points = 53%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;7 points = 47%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;6 points = 40%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;5 points = 33%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;4 points = 27%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;3 points = 20%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;2 points = 13%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;1 point = 7%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:medium;"&gt;0 points = 0%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
