              <descriptionformat>0</descriptionformat>
              <levels>
                <level id="46440">
                  <score>0.00000</score>
                  <definition>Comments show a lack of understanding and/or little to no preparation. Responses were irrelevant to the discussion.</definition>
                  <definitionformat>0</definitionformat>
                </level>
                <level id="46441">
                  <score>3.00000</score>
                  <definition>The discussion question was not thoughtfully answered and/or there are minimal examples of understanding of topics and readings.  Responses to others are minimal.</definition>
                  <definitionformat>0</definitionformat>
                </level>
                <level id="46442">
                  <score>4.00000</score>
                  <definition>The discussion question was at least partially addressed in a thoughtful manner, and there are clear examples of understanding of topics and readings.  Responses to others were sufficient.</definition>
